### Test du profil (remplacer <token> par le token reçu)
GET http://localhost:3000/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Test de changement de mot de passe
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/change-password
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "password123",
  "newPassword": "newpassword123"
}

### Test de mise à jour du profil
PATCH http://localhost:3000/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Updated First Name",
  "lastName": "Updated Last Name",
  "email": "updated@example.com"
}

### Test de création d'utilisateur (Admin uniquement)
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "firstName": "New",
  "lastName": "User",
  "role": "USER"
}

### Test de liste des utilisateurs (Admin uniquement)
GET http://localhost:3000/users
